nodes.text: The Singing Mountain Clan was a Dathomiri Witch clan village located near the Singing Mountain on Dathomir and a bitter rival of the Nightsister clan. Its leader was Augwynne Djo. Gethzerion, the daughter of Augwynne Djo and the founder of the Nightsisters, used to be part of this clan before she was exiled for attempting to kill her mother.
